data.description:
Move-in ready rambler. Beautiful kitchen with espresso-stained cabinets, contrasting glass tile backsplash. Stone countertops, stainless steel appliances and RO system. Open-concept with vault ceiling. New LVP flooring extends through main living areas, laundry & hallway. 3BR upstairs, 2BR down. Primary suite with WIC & private 3/4 BA. 2nd BR with rock-climbing wall & mountain mural. Laundry/mudroom as you enter from the 3-stall, heated garage. 
Lower level completed in 2023. 8' ceilings, corner gas FP, dry bar. Stylish 3/4 bathroom features fully-tiled walk-in shower w/ rain head & wand. Lower-level walks out to a fully fenced back yard, dog-friendly. Extra-wide gate to the front yard, gate to the pond behind. Garden shed, swing-set, chicken coup. Tranquil koi pond, established fruit & flower gardens encircle the home.
